snippet.title: The Game of Life: Vacations - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Pack your bags and whisk away your family and friends on a magical adventure, in The Game of Life: Vacations! Get ready to get lost in the first digital-only spin-off of the beloved Hasbro board game classic.

Download it here:
App Store: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/the-game-of-life-vacations/id1465749734 
Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.marmalade.golv

Follow us:
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/MarmaladeGameStudio/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/MarmaladeGames
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/marmaladegames/
